title: Saturday Night Live Season 10 Complete
description:
SNL Season 10 (1984-1985)

This Season Was Actually The Last Time Dick Ebersol Would Be The Executive Producer. Before Lorne Michaels Would Come Back As The Executive Producer 1 Year Later. It Was A Short Lived Season. After 10th Season. Executive Producer Dick Ebersol. His Entire Cast. And Some Of His Writers Had Left The Show. For Good.

Billy Crystal,Christopher Guest,Rich Hall,Harry Shearer (From The Orginal SNL),Martin Short,Pamela Stephenson Joins The Cast Along With Mary Gross,Julia Louis Dreyfuss,James Jim  Belushi,And Gary Kroger

And Eddie Murphy Also Makes A Return To Host The Christmas Show. For One Last Time On The Show.

So Here Comes Season 10.

2. Bob Uecker - Peter Wolf (10/13/84)
